title: League says I've played 7 out of 10 ranked games but I only played 6.
body: When I click on my profile and go to ranked stats, it says I've played 7 out of 10 ranked games but I knew that I only played 6 games. So i went to check on [oce.op.gg](http://oce.op.gg) and it says I've played 6 games. 2 win 4 loss (I know, I'm a noob XD). BUT THEN I went to check on [lolking](http://www.lolking.com) and it says 7 games played, 2 win 5 loss** (WHAT!!)**. i then clicked on ranked stats on lolking and there were only 6 tabs (Rumble, Jayce, Lee Sin, Ezreal, Riven, Lucian). WHY IS THIS??

replies.body:
Well, how many games have you actually played? Like, what do you remember?

Was this during sometime last week where you had the games, or was it all contained with the last two days?
over the season i've played 6 games

Hm.

Well, not that it really matters. If it's been recorded as a null game, then it won't contribute towards your final placement (ie. you only had to play nine provisionals instead of ten). If you really want to, you can make a [support ticket](https://support.leagueoflegends.com/anonymous_requests/new) and see if the red can set things straight.

Best of luck.
